						Send me an e-mail if you want to talk about cooking, coding or crushing weights.
						Thanks for coming by.
						<br>
						<br>
						-Adam ð“…‚

					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>University of California, Davis - B.S. Computer Science</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
